    <template id="poi_home_content" name="Home Point">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <div id="wrap" class="homepage">
                <!-- Slider with access control for public and retail users. Both visible for web designers -->
                <t t-call="theme_point_sport.poi_home_carousel_b2c" groups="website.group_website_designer, base.group_public"/>
                <strong>
                    <p class="text-center mt32 mb32" groups="website.group_website_designer">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-down"/> Carousel B2B ------------ Carousel B2C <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-up"/>
                    </p>
                </strong>
                <t t-call="theme_point_sport.poi_home_carousel_b2b" groups="website.group_website_designer, base.group_portal"/>
                <!-- Content section -->
                <section class="oe_structure oe_empty"/>
                <t t-call="website_blog_base.s_latest_post"/>
                <section class="oe_structure oe_empty"/>
                <div class="container" groups="website.group_website_designer, base.group_public">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12 mt32 mb32">
                            <h1 class="text-center mb32">Point Sport</h1>
                            <p>Point Sport is a multisport store brand that is currently present with more than 140 stores in Spain, focused on <strong> small </strong> and medium-sized retail specialized in sports.</p>
                            <h2>Do you want to open your Point Sport sports store?</h2>
                            <p>If you want to start and open your specialist store in the sports <strong> sector </strong>, or you already have one and want to access more competitive prices with complete freedom of programming, this is your project. <strong> Point Sport </strong> will allow you to compete on price and product with the rest of stores and supermarkets.</p>
                            <p>You will find a large selection of sporting goods, with more than 100 leading brands in the sports world; <i> Adidas, Umbro, Munich, New Balance, Row, Puma, Converse </i>, and many more. And a wide variety of articles from the main sports disciplines; <i> football, running, training, fitness, basketball, swimming, tennis / paddle, volleyball </i>, etc.</p>
                            <h2>What are the main advantages?</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Experience in the sports market</li>
                                <li>Access to leading sports brands</li>
                                <li>Discounts on wholesale purchase (Anzamar Group)</li>
                                <li>Shipping in 24/48 hours</li>
                                <li>Guaranteed return system</li>
                                <li>Access to exclusive offers and products</li>
                                <li>Freedom to buy without minimum or maximum amounts</li>
                                <li>Marketing and communication support</li>
                                <li>Access to dropshipping</li>
                                <li>Personal attention to the associate</li>
                                <li>Commercial specialists throughout Spain</li>
                                <li>Zone Exclusivity</li>
                                <li>Shopping days to share experiences and access special offers</li>
                                <li>Growing sector and high demand</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>If you want more information about <strong> Point Sport </strong> and set up your own store, you can see the <a href="/page/open_shop#opem_section">how to open a store </a> section or write to <a href="mailto:info@anzamar.com" target="_blank">info@anzamar.com</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
